Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:44.45,EDCNchs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}即便天涯两隔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:47.05,EDCNchs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}即便身无一物
