Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:17.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}Remember you're braver
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.38,0:02:20.01,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}遥かなる道を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:23.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}積み重なる悲しみを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:27.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}きみと生きよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:32.27,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(167,167)}僅かな望みを
